reviews.review_text:
Loving this matrix of this show Takes me right back to the Forum, on a very good Sunday night in 1989.  

Everybody got off this night for sure.  

The band was flying high.  Everyone was on the edge of their seats waiting for DarkStar, and the crowd was jacked up.  High energy throughout, particularly the China>Rider and I'm a Man.

I'm giving this 5 stars because I love this matrix; it improves the listening experience immensely for me.
